Author: cockroach-party <social@cockroachparty.org>
Date:   Mon Jul 20 20:26:20 2026 +0530

    feat: slug availability UX, missed-call bridge, outcome ledger, design polish
    
    WEEK2: Full feature set implementation
    
    Part A - Slug Availability UX:
    - Add GET /links/check-slug endpoint with rate limiting (100/min per IP)
    - Live slug checker with 400ms debounce in FreeLinkGenerator
    - Show green check when available, red X with 3 auto-suggestions when taken
    - Add Title field: friendly nickname for links in dashboard
    - Custom slug input on both free-link and dashboard create forms
    
    Part B - Missed-Call Bridge:
    - New DB tables: missed_calls, leads (source of truth for outcomes)
    - POST /webhooks/missed-call endpoint with shared-secret auth
    - Pluggable SMS interface (stub/msg91/twilio), sends auto-reply with default link
    - Missed Calls tab in dashboard showing source=missed_call leads
    - MacroDroid setup docs in api/README.md with step-by-step instructions
    
    Part C - Outcome-Based Lead Ledger:
    - Leads API: GET /leads (filter by source/status), POST, PATCH
    - Dashboard Leads tab with inline-editable status dropdown and ₹ value
    - Overview tab with total leads, won count, total value, leads-by-source bar chart
    - Status: new → contacted → quoted → won/lost
    
    Part D - Design Polish:
    - Replace ALL emoji icons with lucide-react (Check, X, Copy, etc.)
    - Hover states with 150-300ms transitions on all interactive elements
    - cursor-pointer on buttons and clickable elements
    - Focus rings (ring-2 ring-bottle-green) on form inputs
    - Tab-based dashboard navigation (Overview, Links, Leads, Missed Calls)
    - Consistent honest-ledger design system: paper #FAF7F2, ink #1C1917, terracotta/bottle-green
    
